      "line": 88,
      "message": "there need to be one single command to do all downloading. Seems download.py requires many parameters. So either one single command here or wrapper shell script.\n\nThe main way should be doing downloading with single command. It's also required for CI.\n\nAfter all the main new feature the new download scripts has is the possibility to start it again at any point. So if failure occurs one can check/fix something and just start the download again and script will fast go to the place where it was and continues.\n\nInstructing downloading as multiple steps in below can be done but it should not be the preferred way. (maybe put to appendix?)",
